Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:03.16,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}あの日の蒸気に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:10.70,opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}多くを失って
